{
  "title": "bh telemetry",
  "uid": "bh-telemetry",
  "tags": [
    "bh",
    "observaloop"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 3,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "bh_hive",
        "label": "rig",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "query": "label_values(bh_hive)",
        "allValue": ".*",
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "bh_worktree",
        "label": "worktree",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "query": "label_values(bh_worktree)",
        "allValue": ".*",
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "flow_window",
        "label": "flow window",
        "type": "custom",
        "query": "5m,15m,1h,1d",
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "5m",
            "value": "5m",
            "selected": false
          },
          {
            "text": "15m",
            "value": "15m",
            "selected": false
          },
          {
            "text": "1h",
            "value": "1h",
            "selected": true
          },
          {
            "text": "1d",
            "value": "1d",
            "selected": false
          }
        ],
        "current": {
          "text": "1h",
          "value": "1h",
          "selected": true
        },
        "includeAll": false,
        "multi": false
      }
    ]
  },
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "__comment_metric_names": "PromQL below queries the OTLP instruments from beadhive/otel.py as ingested by the otel-lgtm Prometheus: dots->underscores, counters gain _total, second-unit histograms gain _seconds and a _bucket series. Source instruments: bh.cli.invocations, bh.cli.duration, bh.mcp.tool.invocations, bh.mcp.tool.duration, bh.errors. Resource/attribute labels: bh.hive, bh.worktree, observaloop.profile, bh.cli.command, bh.cli.outcome, bh.mcp.tool, bh.error.boundary, bh.error.kind. Commit-Flow (hqfy) instruments: bh.work.cycle_time(.active), bh.work.stage.<coding|review_wait|merge_latency>, bh.work.rework.count, bh.work.merge_slot.<wait|hold>, bh.work.validation.duration, bh.work.merge.outcome, bh.worktree.op.duration; flow attrs bh.merge.kind, bh.merge.how, bh.work.phase, bh.validation.result, bh.worktree.op, bh.worktree.outcome. NOTE: bh.bead is NO LONGER a metric label (it rides the verb span via otel.set_bead). Counter panels use increase(...[$flow_window]); the $flow_window var (5m/15m/1h default/1d) windows the count/throughput panels.",
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "RED \u2014 bh CLI (bh.cli.*)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "CLI invocation rate \u2014 bh.cli.invocations by command",
      "description": "Rate (R of RED) of CLI command entries, split by bh.cli.command.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (bh_cli_command) (rate(bh_cli_invocations_total{bh_hive=~\"$bh_hive\", bh_worktree=~\"$bh_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{bh_cli_command}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "CLI error rate \u2014 bh.cli.invocations{bh.cli.outcome=error}",
      "description": "Errors (E of RED) from the CLI invocation counter tagged bh.cli.outcome=error.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 1
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (bh_cli_command) (rate(bh_cli_invocations_total{bh_cli_outcome=\"error\", bh_hive=~\"$bh_hive\", bh_worktree=~\"$bh_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{bh_cli_command}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "CLI duration p95 \u2014 bh.cli.duration",
      "description": "Duration (D of RED) p95 wall time per CLI command from the bh.cli.duration histogram.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 1
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, bh_cli_command) (rate(bh_cli_duration_seconds_bucket{bh_hive=~\"$bh_hive\", bh_worktree=~\"$bh_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{bh_cli_command}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
